# Copy to `.env` and fill in. Without it, the app runs fully offline
# (no Drive sync) and you can still use Export/Import to move decks.
#
# Get a Web OAuth Client ID from Google Cloud Console:
#   APIs & Services -> Credentials -> OAuth client ID -> Web application
#   Authorized JS origins: http://localhost:5173 (+ your deployed URL)
#   Enable the "Google Drive API". Scope used: drive.appdata (hidden app folder).
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
